You're like a mucus worm.

259
00:27:45,800 --> 00:27:50,000
Mother... Mother... Don't go...

260
00:27:50,000 --> 00:27:53,400
Fine. Mother won't go.

261
00:27:54,200 --> 00:27:56,300
Really?

262
00:28:00,000 --> 00:28:03,200
