the honored Medicine Elder has come to our house.

316
00:32:49,400 --> 00:32:52,300
Where would you have met him before?

317
00:32:52,300 --> 00:32:53,800
Medicine Elder.

318
00:32:53,800 --> 00:32:58,000
Didn't you die a long time ago
while fighting the Soul Hall?

319
00:32:58,000 --> 00:32:59,600
Me... die?

320
00:33:03,400 --> 00:33:06,400
No such thing.
Not only were we able to capture Hun Miesheng,

321
00:33:06,400 --> 00:33:09,100
he even mended his past ways
and has become a good person.

322
00:33:09,100 --> 00:33:13,200
Thanks to that,
there are no more evil forces in this world.

323
00:33:13,200 --> 00:33:15,200
No evil forces?

324
00:33:15,200 --> 00:33:17,200
Nephew! Nephew!

325
00:33:17,200 --> 00:33:19,800
Han Feng? Medicine Elder!

326
00:33:19,800 --> 00:33:23,000
Come, nephew. Let me have a drink with you.

327
00:33:23,780 --> 00:33:25,800
Senior Sister and I may be from the same sect,

328
00:33:25,800 --> 00:33:29,200
