329
00:33:29,200 --> 00:33:30,200
Right, Senior?

330
00:33:30,200 --> 00:33:34,700
Indeed. Xiao Yan, your Master Uncle
has been with Medicine Elder the longest.

331
00:33:34,700 --> 00:33:38,000
If you have any questions about Fight Techniques,
you can ask him.

332
00:33:38,000 --> 00:33:42,000
